== 近期工程 ==
2014年5月完工的一项投资达10亿美元的项目为该高速公路在圣费尔南多和橙县之间36英里的路段添加了[[高乘載車道|高乘載車道]]及附属的出入口。<ref>{{cite web| url=http://ktla.com/2014/05/23/new-10-mile-carpool-lane-opens-on-northbound-i-405-in-sepulveda-pass/| title=New 10-Mile Carpool Lane Opens on Northbound I-405 in Sepulveda Pass| publisher=KTLA| date=2014-05-23| accessdate=2014-12-27| archive-date=2019-06-10| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610043520/https://ktla.com/2014/05/23/new-10-mile-carpool-lane-opens-on-northbound-i-405-in-sepulveda-pass/| dead-url=no}}</ref>

